  "title": "Effort",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "When you perform a"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "test"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/t/tests",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/T/tests"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", you"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "commit"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/c/commit",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/C/commit"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "effort. The more effort you commit to a test, the more likely it is to succeed."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Your"
        },
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "committed effort"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "is equal to all effort"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "committed"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/c/commit",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/C/commit"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "from any sources in step 2 of the test."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Your"
        },
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "resulting effort"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "is equal to your committed effort with any modifiers from the"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "challenge card"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/c/challenge_cards",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/C/challenge_cards"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "or other effects applied. When the results of tests and other effects that scale off of the \"effort\" of a test, they scale off of this resulting effort."
        }
      ]
    }
